---
title: Smart Mini Fig-Glazed Turkey Meatloaves with Pan-Tossed Potatoes and Creamy Green Beans
description: Eating smart never tasted so great! Turkey meatloaves are glazed in our sweet fig spread for some golden caramelization. Potatoes are parboiled then tossed in the pan with butter and garlic until crispy, while creamy green beans add a welcome unctuousness to the plate!

